These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, french, italian, mexican, nigerian, thai
1. the egyptian is in the middle##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the italian##1
4. the dutch is on the right of the french##1
5. the thai is on the far left##1
6. the nigerian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | thai | italian | mexican | egyptian | french | dutch | nigerian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, doctor, entrepreneur, librarian, manager, nurse, teacher
1. the teacher is on the far right##1
2. the analyst is on the far left##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the manager##1
4. the manager is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the librarian is on the right of the nurse##1
6. the teacher is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | analyst | manager | entrepreneur | nurse | librarian | doctor | teacher |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, drawing, fishing, rock-climbing, sudoku, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | board-games | sudoku | drawing | woodworking | card-games | fishing |

 #################################
 
