.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard, mouse, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | turtle | hedgehog | lizard | snake | goldfish | guinea-pig | mouse |

