2. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | disaster | crime | sports | horror | thriller | drama |

